{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-index-tsx","path":"/post/windows-shezhi-dingshi-xiumian","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>创建一个基本任务</h2>\n<p>直接按<code class=\"language-text\">win</code>键搜索任务计划程序打开任务计划程序，然后在右侧面板找到创建基本任务</p>\n<p>现在开始创建一个新的任务</p>\n<ul>\n<li>“常规”定义了这个任务的基本信息</li>\n<li>“触发器”定义任何触发这个任务，点击新建便可以选择时间和媒体触发</li>\n<li>“操作”定义要执行的任务，目前只有启动程序这个操作</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>添加睡眠命令</h2>\n<p>在“操作”面板选择浏览，然后会默认打开<code class=\"language-text\">C:\\Windows\\System32</code>这个目录，这个目录下面存在一些列Windows内置程序，直接在上面搜索<code class=\"language-text\">rundll32</code>,然后选择<code class=\"language-text\">rundll32.exe</code>这个程序</p>\n<p>在添加参数一处添加:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-powershell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-powershell\">powrprof<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dll<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>SetSuspendState 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>完整命令:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-powershell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-powershell\">C:\\Windows\\System32\\rundll32<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exe powrprof<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dll<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>SetSuspendState 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>注意：如果你启用了休眠功能这个将会变成休眠而不是睡眠，如果想直接休眠需要零时关闭休眠功能</p>\n<p>和上面步骤一样，不过这个两个命令在上一个命令的前后，面板右侧有个“5”和“6”可以移动任务的位置</p>\n<p>启用休眠和关闭休眠的命令：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-powershell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 关闭休眠</span>\nC:\\Windows\\System32\\powercfg<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exe <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>h off\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 启用休眠</span>\nC:\\Windows\\System32\\powercfg<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exe <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>h on</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 630px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4668b0a7e2aec39b2a51bab6149e75ef/f058b/image-20191030141716689.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 85.71428571428571%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/4668b0a7e2aec39b2a51bab6149e75ef/a42d1/image-20191030141716689.webp 231w,\n/static/4668b0a7e2aec39b2a51bab6149e75ef/a7d21/image-20191030141716689.webp 463w,\n/static/4668b0a7e2aec39b2a51bab6149e75ef/8aab1/image-20191030141716689.webp 630w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/4668b0a7e2aec39b2a51bab6149e75ef/6e622/image-20191030141716689.png 231w,\n/static/4668b0a7e2aec39b2a51bab6149e75ef/71ce0/image-20191030141716689.png 463w,\n/static/4668b0a7e2aec39b2a51bab6149e75ef/f058b/image-20191030141716689.png 630w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/4668b0a7e2aec39b2a51bab6149e75ef/f058b/image-20191030141716689.png\"\n          alt=\"image-20191030141716689\"\n          title=\"image-20191030141716689\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">image-20191030141716689</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>后续</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>任务系统是个很好的东西，可是脑海中没几个可以自动化的想法</li>\n<li>\n<p>可以在任务计获程序库而不是任务计获程序（本地找到）设置的任务</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 925px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/912744df28d3d3e58f269f9b7de1ce47/b97f6/image-20191030142055257.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.943722943722943%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/912744df28d3d3e58f269f9b7de1ce47/a42d1/image-20191030142055257.webp 231w,\n/static/912744df28d3d3e58f269f9b7de1ce47/a7d21/image-20191030142055257.webp 463w,\n/static/912744df28d3d3e58f269f9b7de1ce47/31b98/image-20191030142055257.webp 925w,\n/static/912744df28d3d3e58f269f9b7de1ce47/cb8de/image-20191030142055257.webp 958w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 925px) 100vw, 925px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/912744df28